	(18, 3, 'History Of Ta Lien Son Mountain', 'Ta Lien Son also has another unique name, Co Trau. The mountain range is located in Ta Odd commune, Tam Duong district, Lai Chau province.', '<p>&nbsp;Ta Lien Son also has another unique name, Co Trau. The geological history of Mount Fansipan dates back about 250 million years when it was naturally ranged&nbsp;and is located in Ta Odd commune, Tam Duong district, Lai Chau province. This place is only about 10km from the center of the province. Ta Lien mountain peak is located on the border between 2 provinces Lai Chau &amp; Lao Cai.Co Trau is the 6th highest mountain range in Vietnam with a recorded height at the peak of 2993m. Standing on the top of the mountain, the whole Lai Chau with high mountains, successive terraces, miniature dear roof in sight. At that moment, we felt the beauty of Vietnam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '../admin/assets/img/News/5bb05ab1502f39fc03db39d7cd0491db.jpg', 'king le loi', 'Ta Lien Son also has another unique name, Co Trau. The mountain range is located in Ta Odd commune, Tam Duong district, Lai Chau province. This place is only about 10km from the center of the province. Ta Lien mountain peak is located on the border between 2 provinces Lai Chau & Lao Cai.Co Trau is the 6th highest mountain range in Vietnam with a recorded height at the peak of 2993m. Standing on the top of the mountain, the whole Lai Chau with high mountains, successive terraces, miniature dear roof in sight. At that moment, we felt the beauty of Vietnam.', NULL),
	(19, 3, 'History Of Ta Chi Nhu Mountain', 'back about 250 million years the top of the mountain is as proud as the spine of the buffalo living in the forest at the foot of the mountain...', '<p>The geological history of Mount Ta Chi Nhu&nbsp; dates back about 250 million years when it was naturallyThe road to the top of Ta Chi Nhu, the roof of Yen Bai belongs to the area of X&agrave; Hồ village, Trạm Tấu district. With an altitude of 2979m, Ta Chi Nhu ranked 7th in the top 10 highest mountains in Vietnam &ndash; one of the ideal cloud hunting locations, also known as &quot; Cloud Paradise in the Lower World &quot;. Standing on the top of Ta Chi Nhu, just with your hands, you can reach the clouds, immersed in the space like a futuristic place. Many people believe that the clouds not only appear above the head but are at eye level, soft as silk strips covering everywhere. The most special highlight here is probably the field of purple flowers radiant under the clouds in late autumn. It is not difficult to see the majestic mountain ranges covered with a purple star, with a fragrant floral scent, surrounded by goats and horses of indigenous Hmong households grazing. All of them surprise you like stepping out of a poetic natural picture full of fairy tales.</p>\r\n', '../admin/assets/img/News/8086c89472af9d11209e108cc978c5bf.jpg', 'king le loi', 'he roof of Yen Bai belongs to the area of Xà Hồ village, Trạm Tấu district. With an altitude of 2979m, Ta Chi Nhu ranked 7th in the top 10 highest mountains in Vietnam – one of the ideal cloud hunting locations, also known as " Cloud Paradise in the Lower World ". Standing on the top of Ta Chi Nhu, just with your hands, you can reach the clouds, immersed in the space like a futuristic place. Many people believe that the clouds not only appear above the head but are at eye level, soft as silk strips covering everywhere. ', NULL),
	(20, 3, 'History Of Nhiu Co San Mountain', 'The geological history of Mount Fansipan dates back about 250 million years when it was located in Bat Xat district,...', '<p>&nbsp;The geological history of Mount Fansipan dates back about 250 million years when it was&nbsp;located in Bat Xat district, Lao Cai province, the peak of Nhiu Co San mountain is also known as Buffalo Horn. The terrain in Nhiu Co San is very diverse and interesting. The road to the foot of the mountain to start the trek is quite difficult, especially in the rainy season the road is slippery. Originally low hills with shrubs, meadows, and cliffs. Climbing higher, you will enter the primeval forest with tall and large wooden trunks, and maple foliage that looks like a poetic European sky.</p>\r\n', '', 'king le loi', 'located in Bat Xat district, Lao Cai province, the peak of Nhiu Co San mountain is also known as Buffalo Horn. The terrain in Nhiu Co San is very diverse and interesting. The road to the foot of the mountain to start the trek is quite difficult, especially in the rainy season the road is slippery. Originally low hills with shrubs, meadows, and cliffs. Climbing higher, you will enter the primeval forest with tall and large wooden trunks, and maple foliage that looks like a poetic European sky.', 'd'),
	(21, 3, 'History Of Nhiu Co San Mountain', 'The geological history of Mount Fansipan dates back about 250 million years when it was located in Bat Xat district, Lao Cai province...', '<p>The geological history of Mount Fansipan dates back about 250 million years when it was&nbsp;located in Bat Xat district, Lao Cai province, the peak of Nhiu Co San mountain is also known as Buffalo Horn. The terrain in Nhiu Co San is very diverse and interesting. The road to the foot of the mountain to start the trek is quite difficult, especially in the rainy season the road is slippery. Originally low hills with shrubs, meadows, and cliffs. Climbing higher, you will enter the primeval forest with tall and large wooden trunks, and maple foliage that looks like a poetic European sky</p>\r\n', '../admin/assets/img/News/4e79caad9df7d69661a381b10a6875bf.jpg', 'king le loi', 'the peak of Nhiu Co San mountain is also known as Buffalo Horn. The terrain in Nhiu Co San is very diverse and interesting. The road to the foot of the mountain to start the trek is quite difficult, especially in the rainy season the road is slippery. Originally low hills with shrubs, meadows, and cliffs. Climbing higher, you will enter the primeval forest with tall and large wooden trunks, and maple foliage that looks like a poetic European sky', NULL),
	(22, 2, 'Sale off the highest climbing tour', 'Our Easter Sale is back. Get 20 % OFF on Any Packages. Use Coupon Code: EASTERDMA20 at checkout!', '<p>The Kadayawan festival is fast approaching. It highlights the greatness of Davao city&rsquo;s diverse cultures, and as such it&rsquo;s a pretty colorful event. The festival is one thing that Davao city is very well-known for, and tourists flock to the city during Kadayawan season. This season also presents a great opportunity to climb the country&rsquo;s&hellip;</p>\r\n', '../admin/assets/img/News/e2cdf139b8b8d9330ffde183e5344679.jpg', 'Nam', '', NULL),
	(23, 2, 'Get 20% off when booking tours online', 'Interested in trying an alternative outdoor experience? Get 20% off when booking tours online', '<p>Interested in trying an alternative outdoor experience? Rock climbing is one of the best options available in Olympos. The area is famous for having some perfect climbing spots and attracts every year many visitors wishing to explore the imposing cliffs. Get ready to try something new or exercise your rock climbing skills with an unforgettable experience in Olympos. The activity is ideal for people of all ages and promises many fun moments full of laughter and adrenaline boosts.</p>\r\n', '../admin/assets/img/News/58cb25006319a2b2f8ec5edd82ea85b4.jpg', 'Nam', '', NULL),
	(24, 2, 'Up to 10% off book group tour', 'This incredible group Climbing Tour experience begins with a pickup service from your place of accommodation', '<p>This incredible group Climbing Tour experience begins with a pickup service from your place of accommodation. Members of our team will drive you towards the rock climbing station, with a comfortable and modern car. The spot is not really far but during the ride you can observe some nice views over the area.<br />\r\nIn case this is your first time trying rock climbing, there is nothing to worry about. When you arrive at the area where the activity takes place, you will meet a team of professional rock climbing instructors. Before the activity, the instructors will offer you a brief, yet detailed introduction on rock climbing. More precisely, they will explain how to climb, how to use the equipment, and which are the safety rules. Then, they will distribute the equipment and assist you in using it.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '../admin/assets/img/News/1b413657f5a143401502ed307702c3d2.png', 'Nam', '', NULL),
	(25, 2, 'Sale off Lunar new year 30%', 'Sale off Lunar new year 30%. The cliffs are not stiff. In other words, the level of difficulty is low to average', '<p>The cliffs are not stiff. In other words, the level of difficulty is low to average. Thus, if you are an experienced rock climber it is still a fun activity to do. Accompanied by the instructors, you will start climbing on the rocks and feel the first adrenaline boosts. Rock climbing is a fun yet interesting activity as it requires concentration and attention to details. It is also a great bonding activity for groups of friends or families as it requires cooperation and gives you the opportunity to create many precious memories together. Please note that children can participate as well, given that they are above the defined age limit.</p>\r\n', '../admin/assets/img/News/3450fbeda8cc6ba4eba88a7ff8adc478.jpg', 'Nam', '', NULL),
	(26, 2, 'Tour Fansipan up to 40% off', 'Fansipan - the highest mountain in Vietnam, is not only dubbed the "roof of Indochina" but also a symbol of conquest', '<p>Fansipan - the highest mountain in Vietnam, is not only dubbed the &quot;roof of Indochina&quot; but also a symbol of conquest of youth and determination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fansipan climbing route is quite diverse landscape, enough for you to have a trip full of experience. The main terrain is a trail through the forest with steep climbs clinging to sturdy stainless steel ladders. The journey therefore also becomes easier and more common for most people to conquer.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '../admin/assets/img/News/4a6fa0d997a83f1fcb630b71ca286d3e.jpg', 'Nam', '', NULL),
	(27, 2, 'Off 50% for membership', 'Once you reach the top of the cliff you will be amazed by the spectacular views.', '<p>Once you reach the top of the cliff you will be amazed by the spectacular views. Also, you will be full of emotions and proudness because of your achievement. Then, you will start descending the rock, which is way more fun! At the end, when this incredible experience is over, a car will drive you back to your place of accommodation. The Rock Climbing Tour is surely an incredible experience in Olympos not to be missed!</p>\r\n', '../admin/assets/img/News/c746bd9a9ce2bb758fd5f9999b75ae26.jpg', 'Nam', '', NULL);

