	(7, 1, 'LEO NÚI CHINH PHỤC FANSIPAN', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-03 00:00:00', 111, 20, 'Sapa Lào Cai', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/3488a1ee904fac56d8705e807b676930.jpg', '1', 'Trekking Fansipan is going to be a journey for visitors to challenge...', 'Trekking Fansipan is going to be a journey for visitors to challenge, to break through their limits. During the Fansipan trekking tour 2 days and 1 night, visitors will admire the majestic Hoang Lien range kneeling on top of each other in the green of mountains and forests, full of majestic clouds and touching the roof of Indochina.', 'd'),
	(8, 1, 'LEO NUI CHINH PHUC PU SI LUNG', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-05 00:00:00', 255, 30, 'Lai Châu', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/ce28696fd0f01c92b3997ae608c57f96.jpg', '1', 'he journey to conquer Pusilung will definitely bring arduous challenges and bring...', 'The journey to conquer Pusilung will definitely bring arduous challenges and bring memorable experiences. The route climbs along large streams with many rapids. When you reach an altitude of 2800m, you will encounter mark 42 – one of the highest border milestones of Vietnam. From the 42nd mark, there are nearly 17km more forest roads to reach the top. ', NULL),
	(9, 1, 'LEO NÚI CHINH PHỤC PU SI LUNG', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-05 00:00:00', 255, 30, 'Lai Châu', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/a3c479b448f3d2ac4579bf9fd129cc3d.jpg', '1', 'he journey to conquer Pusilung will definitely bring arduous challenges and bring...', 'The journey to conquer Pusilung will definitely bring arduous challenges and bring memorable experiences. The route climbs along large streams with many rapids. When you reach an altitude of 2800m, you will encounter mark 42 – one of the highest border milestones of Vietnam. From the 42nd mark, there are nearly 17km more forest roads to reach the top. ', 'd'),
	(10, 1, 'LEO NUI CHINH PHUC PUTALENG', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-04 00:00:00', 195, 40, 'Lai Châu.', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/abe5dcc49e2bcb1717b5506d841f8214.jpg', '1', 'experience the journey through the primeval forest in Tam Duong district, Lai Chau province...', 'experience the journey through the primeval forest in Tam Duong district, Lai Chau province. Pu Ta Leng\'s specialty is the cool streams and thousands of azaleas every spring.', NULL),
	(11, 1, 'LEO NÚI CHINH PHỤC PUTALENG', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-04 00:00:00', 195, 40, 'huyện Tam Đường, tỉnh Lai Châu.', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/33d2eb1173094242f8b2c992d4c44e01.jpg', '1', 'experience the journey through the primeval forest in Tam Duong district, Lai Chau province...', 'experience the journey through the primeval forest in Tam Duong district, Lai Chau province. Pu Ta Leng\'s specialty is the cool streams and thousands of azaleas every spring.', 'd'),
	(12, 1, 'TOUR BACH MOC LUONG TU', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-04 00:00:00', 191, 50, ' Lào Cai', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/a82464fcffd4cdb27a2e454e5fa63858.jpg', '3', 'Bach Moc Peak with an altitude of 3046m is the 4th highest mountain of Vietnam...', 'Bach Moc Peak with an altitude of 3046m is the 4th highest mountain of Vietnam, the natural boundary of 2 provinces Lai Chau and Lao Cai.  It can be said that "dawn in the clouds" has become the brand of the mountain named Bach Moc. The terrain of Bach Moc is quite diverse and difficult, requiring you to prepare skills and good physical foundation. However, the value of the beautiful scenery here is always commensurate with the effort that you have to spend when conquering this peak.', NULL),
	(13, 1, 'TOUR TA LIEN SON', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-03 00:00:00', 164, 40, 'Lai Châu', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/6c606788be2c97d69c5073df368934b8.jpg', '2', 'the top of the mountain is as proud as the spine of the buffalo living in the forest at the foot of the mountain, so Ta Lien is also known as The Buffalo Neck....', 'the top of the mountain is as proud as the spine of the buffalo living in the forest at the foot of the mountain, so Ta Lien is also known as The Buffalo Neck. The recorded elevation on Ta Lien peak is 2996m above sea level. From above, you can see the small but beautiful city of Lai Chau among four majestic mountains and forests.  Ta Lien forest with diverse primary vegetation will make you overwhelmed and excited. You seem to get lost in the mysterious fairytale scene with ancient trees, moss and ferns covered, creeping trunks clinging to stone slabs stacked with all sorts of strange shapes, carpets of white fallen camellias, fiery red maple leaves and green moss carpets that charm a fresh color.', NULL),
	(14, 1, 'TOUR TA CHI NHU', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-03 00:00:00', 165, 60, 'Yên Bái ', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/7dacc0ea9f181fd5b24d8c85615a0ee1.jpg', '2', 'The road to the top of Ta Chi Nhu, the roof of Yen Bai belongs to the area of Xà Hồ village, Trạm Tấu district...', 'The road to the top of Ta Chi Nhu, the roof of Yen Bai belongs to the area of Xà Hồ village, Trạm Tấu district. With an altitude of 2979m, Ta Chi Nhu ranked 7th in the top 10 highest mountains in Vietnam – one of the ideal cloud hunting locations, also known as " Cloud Paradise in the Lower World ". Standing on the top of Ta 	Chi Nhu, just with your hands, you can reach the clouds, immersed in the space like a futuristic place. Many people believe that the clouds not only appear above the head but are at eye level, soft as silk strips covering everywhere. The most special highlight here is probably the field of purple flowers radiant under the clouds in late autumn. It is not difficult to see the majestic mountain ranges covered with a purple star, with a fragrant floral scent, surrounded by goats and horses of indigenous Hmong households grazing. All of them surprise you like stepping out of a poetic natural picture full of fairy tales.', NULL),
	(15, 1, 'TOUR NHIU CO SAN ', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-03 00:00:00', 155, 100, ' Lào Cai', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/b2539d78053f82a57b344d6dfb448bdf.jpg', '2', 'Located in Bat Xat district, Lao Cai province, the peak of Nhiu Co San mountain is also known as Buffalo Horn....', 'Located in Bat Xat district, Lao Cai province, the peak of Nhiu Co San mountain is also known as Buffalo Horn. The terrain in Nhiu Co San is very diverse and interesting. The road to the foot of the mountain to start the trek is quite difficult, especially in the rainy season the road is slippery. Originally low hills with shrubs, meadows and cliffs. Climbing higher, you will enter the primeval forest with tall and large wooden trunks, maple foliage that looks like a poetic European sky.', NULL),
	(16, 3, 'Camping in Dau Tieng lake', '2022-11-16 00:00:00', '2022-11-18 00:00:00', 250, 10, 'Tay Ninh', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/3441e5abc9a619049a4b3fbddd4f22c3.jpg', '1', 'Dau Tieng Lake is one of the largest artificial lakes in Vietnam and Southeast Asia', 'Dau Tieng Lake is one of the largest artificial lakes in Vietnam and Southeast Asia. Which province is Dau Tieng Lake in? Actually, Dau Tieng lake has a geographical position adjacent to 3 provinces of Binh Duong, Binh Phuoc and Tay Ninh, but mainly belongs to Tay Ninh part. Dau Tieng Lake area up to 27 m², capacity to hold 1.58 billion m³ of water, catchment area of ​​2700 km² and 45.6 km² of semi-submerged land, built on April 29, 1981 and completed on January 10, 1985. With unspoiled beauty equally poetic, fresh nature surrounded in cool and peaceful air, Dau Tieng Lake becomes a tourist destination not to be missed. Overnight camping trips are also often held here, especially in the area of ​​Dau Tieng Lake in Binh Duong because the location is not too far from Saigon, it only takes about 2 hours, it is very convenient for moving and there are many beaches. Camping, watching the sunrise is very beautiful.', NULL),
	(17, 3, 'Camping in Red maple forest', '2022-11-16 00:00:00', '2022-11-19 00:00:00', 200, 5, 'Da Lat', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/defb9e8e75cf07c473d5a4a9c0ab4930.jpg', '2', 'You will get romantic experiences like in love movies when you join the Red Maple Forest', 'Usually we only see the red maple forest scene in Korean movies, but now when camping at Dalat\'s Red Maple Forest resort, you will also experience the scenery. The beautiful nature is not inferior to the scenes in the movies.  The poetic, romantic scenery with natural trees in harmony with the lake and the presence of many rare and fancy plants have a strange attraction for any visitor when coming here. Because this landscape brings us away from the noisy and bustling life of the city to immerse ourselves in the beautiful nature and unforgettable moments during the camping process.', NULL),
	(18, 1, 'TOUR KHANG SU VAN', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-07 00:00:00', 2000, 10, 'Lai Châu', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/2a362bbe73bf662c332fa102939ff03b.jpg', '2', 'Khang Su Van Peak is likened to a natural wall protecting the northern boundary of our country...', 'Khang Su Van Peak is likened to a natural wall protecting the northern boundary of our country. This peak is also located among the highest peaks in Vietnam, it belongs to Phong Tho district, Lai Chau province. Possessing an altitude of 3,012m above sea level, the mountain range stands firmly protecting the northern airspace. Khang Su Van is covered with thousand-year-old forests and extremely rich vegetation. In particular, if you want to conquer this peak, you need to have a license from Ma Chai Golden Border Guard Station. Although the journey is a bit difficult, ReviewNao is sure that you will find a poetic interesting feeling here.', NULL),
	(19, 3, 'Camping in Dasar valley', '2022-11-18 00:00:00', '2022-11-19 00:00:00', 150, 7, 'Da Lat', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/7f8b3b0ebb0d8b1ccddd020c40d857cc.jpg', '3', 'Camping is one of the most favorite activities of tourists when traveling in Dasar valley', 'In the evening, on the lawn, people together light a fire, eat and sing in the vast space of heaven and earth. After that, they will sit together and watch the starry sky, tell each other funny stories without beginning or end, and feel the thin layers of cold mist surrounding them, take a deep breath. The fresh, fragrant air of old pine needles and flowers are everywhere.  Joy is sometimes simple but not always available, if you have the opportunity to come to the beautiful Dasar valley, let\'s camp together overnight in the open air and enjoy moments of fun but no less. this romantic sweet part.', NULL),
	(20, 3, 'Camping in Tuyen Lam lake', '2022-11-17 00:00:00', '2022-11-20 00:00:00', 300, 15, 'Da Lat', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/9895eccf3419bbbec5321486f7ca29ae.jpg', '1', 'Tuyen Lam Lake has a peaceful beauty with a calm lake surface dotted with poetic features', 'About 6km south of the city center, Tuyen Lam Lake is located in Ward 4, Da Lat City, Lam Dong Province. Owning an area of more than 350 hectares and a depth of over 30m in some places, the lake water flows through the dam like a magical and charming waterfall. This beauty has "fevered" many people back and forth to admire the quiet, poetic scene. As the city\'s largest freshwater lake, standing here, you can magnify the view of the three-leaf pine forest covering the majestic hill. The natural scenery here has been carefully blended together, sketching a masterpiece of art that will capture the hearts of professional artists or photographers.', NULL),
	(21, 1, 'TOUR CHUNG NHIA VU', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-03 00:00:00', 200, 30, 'Lai Châu', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/e62be5fe113141ec13d8da5b4933a7d1.jpg', '2', 'This peak is located in Phong Tho district, Lai Chau province, it is located at an altitude of 2,918m above sea level. The way to the top of the mountain is not too difficult, most of the short paths go through the bamboo forest and bamboo forest....', 'This peak is located in Phong Tho district, Lai Chau province, it is located at an altitude of 2,918m above sea level. The way to the top of the mountain is not too difficult, most of the short paths go through the bamboo forest and bamboo forest. his peak is located in Phong Tho district, Lai Chau province, it is located at an altitude of 2,918m above sea level. The way to the top of the mountain is not too difficult, most of the short paths go through the bamboo forest and bamboo forest.', NULL),
	(22, 3, 'Camping amid clouds Ta Xua', '2022-11-20 00:00:00', '2022-11-22 00:00:00', 100, 9, 'Son La', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/38b43a06104318cedc4e3130ad6c68f2.jpg', '3', 'Pitching a tent and sleeping overnight on top of Ta Xua Mountain is an interesting travel experience', 'Situated 230 kilometers (143 miles) north of Hanoi, Ta Xua, one of the highest peaks in Vietnam at 2,865 meters, straddles Yen Bai and Son La provinces. A trail leading to the peak, called Dinosaur’s Spine, at 1,600 meters above sea level has become increasingly popular among trekkers as a cloud-hunting spot in recent years, but the journey there is not easy at all with dangerous winding routes and craggy cliffs. If you choose to set up a tent along the trail, remember to take warm clothes and an insect repellent, and buy firewood from locals to burn at night. It is necessary to buy food in advance because there are no restaurants or other services on the mountain. From late November the temperature in Ta Xua is 14-19 degrees Celsius during the day and 9-10 degrees at night. The best time to hunt for clouds there is from December to March.', NULL),
	(23, 3, 'Camping Na Hang lake', '2022-11-21 00:00:00', '2022-11-25 00:00:00', 260, 13, 'Tuyen Quang', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/7d6f54ff64b56f6ea888c2cc54c00be5.jpg', '1', 'Na Hang Lake in the northern province of Tuyen Quang is an emerging tourist destination', 'Located 110km north of Tuyen Quang City, the lake is the meeting place of the Gam and Nang rivers. The lake is scattered with nearly 100 mountains creating an imposing landscape. Tourists can experience fishing, cooking by the lake, camping, driving bamboo boats and kayaking. The lake covers a total area of 8,000ha, which is like a giant mirror reflecting sunlight in the turquoise water. Coc Vai Mountain, an iconic image of the area. The name in local language means "a pilar to tie up a buffalo" recalling a legend of a giant hero, who tied up his buffalo here to build a dam to store water for the villagers.  When it gets dark, the lake reflects the lights from the floating boats of fishermen. Tourists can watch fishing at night and enjoy the sunrise early in the morning.', NULL),
	(24, 2, 'EXPLORE TRANG AN CAVE ', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-03 00:00:00', 40, 0, 'Ninh Bình', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/a2ea2c0f9904c97ac0d1523a575ee8cc.jpeg', '1', 'Trang An is a famous Ninh Binh tourist destination located more than 80km from Hanoi. This eco-tourism area is located in both Gia Lu and Gia Vien districts ...', 'Trang An is a famous Ninh Binh tourist destination located more than 80km from Hanoi. This eco-tourism area is located in both Gia Lu and Gia Vien districts and part of Ninh Binh city. This complex of rocks and caves covers an area of more than 1,000 hectares with 31 water valleys and 48 trans-water caves with a total length of about 20 km. Winding at the foot of limestone mountains, around primeval forests and reed forests, the charming landscape has created a beautiful picture of nature. Visitors to Trang An are very interested in sightseeing journeys by rowing boat. Through the caves, you will experience the excitement and thrill of going deep into the cave.', NULL),
	(25, 3, 'Camping Ba Vi', '2022-11-17 00:00:00', '2022-11-18 00:00:00', 140, 20, 'Ha Noi', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/e51ad0f334660fb5cebe715b71519806.jpg', '1', 'Coming to the Mount Ba Vi, you can enjoy the fresh air while camping or trekking', 'Ba Vi National Park is only about 60km from Hanoi, with vegetation diversity, fresh and cool air will be a great weekend outing trip for families and young people who want to escape from the bustling of capital city. Coming to the Mount Ba Vi, you can enjoy the fresh air while camping or trekking, those who love photography will also be passionate about because the scenery is very beautiful with outstanding places such as pine forests, ancient church… Summer and autumn – from April to November, is the best time you should travel to Ba Vi mountain. Because, the summer atmosphere in the city is very hot and stuffy, but just setting foot on Ba Vi, you will feel like stepping into a completely different world: fresh air, cool and especially very quiet. You should pay attention to avoid rainy days because ramps, slippery and very easy to fall. In the winter, it is cold and foggy, which will affect your vision. However, winter on Ba Vi also has its own beauty, just if you like to go, you can pick up your backpack and go to Ba Vi.', NULL),
	(26, 2, 'Dau Go Cave', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-04 00:00:00', 100, 1, 'Hạ Long', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/6c8378bc09169b9710e81394bc2fd048.jpg', '3', 'About 5000m2 wide, Dau Go Cave is located at an altitude of 27m above sea level at the same age to form Thien Cung Cave – late Pleixtocene about 2 million years ago...', 'About 5000m2 wide, Dau Go Cave is located at an altitude of 27m above sea level at the same age to form Thien Cung Cave – late Pleixtocene about 2 million years ago. Dau Go Cave seems to gather an ancient architectural complex. Exuding an ancient, wild and still beauty with many stone pillars, stone pillars, stalagmites small, soaring as if to reach the blue sky ... The cave has a rich diversity of flora and fauna', NULL),
	(27, 2, 'Phong Nha Ke Bang Cave', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-04 00:00:00', 11, 20, 'Quảng Bình ', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/f3d34e5dd87b8a7a2924a1de3c71a36f.jpg', '1', 'Phong Nha Ke Bang National Park is a famous landmark that has been recognized by UNESCO...', 'Phong Nha Ke Bang National Park is a famous landmark that has been recognized by UNESCO as a world natural heritage, attracting thousands of visitors to Quang Binh every year.  Phong Nha - Ke Bang is one of the two largest limestone mountains in the world with a complex of more than 300 rich and small caves, known as the "Cave Kingdom" containing the beautiful beauty of creation.  Especially the system of underground rivers and hundreds of rare species of animals and plants exists, including many species named in the Red Book of Vietnam and the world is a paradise for cave scientists, explorers and tourists.', NULL),
	(28, 2, 'Sung Sot Cave ', '2022-11-01 00:00:00', '2022-11-02 00:00:00', 10000, 30, 'Yên Bái ', '../admin/assets/img/Tour/9730b4725e8ff271b07ba16693166767.jpg', '3', 'The road to the sung sot cave  , the roof of Yen Bai belongs to the area of Xà Hồ village, Trạm Tấu district...', 'Bach Moc Peak with an altitude of 3046m is the 4th highest mountain of Vietnam, the natural boundary of 2 provinces Lai Chau and Lao Cai.  It can be said that "dawn in the clouds" has become the brand of the mountain named Bach Moc. The terrain of Bach Moc is quite diverse and difficult, requiring you to prepare skills and good physical foundation. However, the value of the beautiful scenery here is always commensurate with the effort that you have to spend when conquering this peak.', NULL);

